02780 UINT8 GetTraversability( INT16 sStartSector, INT16 sEndSector )
02781 {
02782       UINT8 ubDirection = 0;
02783       INT16 sDifference = 0;
02784 
02785       // given start and end sectors
02786       sDifference = sEndSector - sStartSector;
02787 
02788 
02789       if( sDifference == -1 )
02790       {
02791             ubDirection = WEST_STRATEGIC_MOVE;
02792       }
02793       else if( sDifference == 1 )
02794       {
02795             ubDirection = EAST_STRATEGIC_MOVE;
02796       }
02797       else if( sDifference == 16 )
02798       {
02799             ubDirection = SOUTH_STRATEGIC_MOVE;
02800       }
02801       else
02802       {
02803             ubDirection = NORTH_STRATEGIC_MOVE;
02804       }
02805 
02806 
02807       return( SectorInfo[ sStartSector ].ubTraversability[ ubDirection ] );
02808 }
